---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" current="/about">
  <article class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl px-4 pt-10 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--accent)] mb-2">$ whoami</h1>
    <hr class="border-[var(--border)] mb-8" />

    <p class="text-[var(--foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
      I work on low-level software, embedded systems, and bugs that somehow disappear the moment you add logging.
    </p>

    <p class="text-[var(--foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-8">
      This blog is my logbook: things I built, things I broke, and the notes I’d rather save than painfully rediscover later.
    </p>

    <blockquote class="mb-8 border-l-[3px] border-[var(--accent)] pl-5 text-[var(--text-dim)]">
      <p class="leading-relaxed">“One accurate measurement is worth a thousand expert opinions.”</p>
      <footer class="mt-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--accent)]">Grace Hopper</footer>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
      <a href="https://github.com/0xbadcaffe" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[var(--muted)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--foreground)] hover:text-white rounded transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a href="https://x.com/0xbadcaffe" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[var(--muted)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--foreground)] hover:text-white rounded transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.744l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.253 5.622 5.911-5.622zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
        X
      </a>
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[var(--muted)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--foreground)] hover:text-white rounded transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 11a9 9 0 0 1 9 9"/><path d="M4 4a16 16 0 0 1 16 16"/><circle cx="5" cy="19" r="1"/></svg>
        RSS
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
      The name is <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hexspeak" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[var(--accent)] underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-2">hexspeak</a> — <code class="text-[var(--accent)]">0xBADCAFFE</code>, bad coffee. Accurate.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
